text: Tara uniharule unala'i jhutho manirakhe, ta hamile unala'i ra jo manisaharu unaka satha dungama savara thi'e, sabaila'i baca'ihalyaum, ra unala'i (dhartiko) uttaradhikari banayaum, ra uniharula'i duba'i diyaum jasale hamro nisanila'i jhutho maneka thi'e, yo hernu parnecha ki juna manisaharula'i savadhana gari'eko thiyo, tiniharuko kasto parinama bhayo
